/* Custom Message Styling */
.info {
  margin: 15px 0;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #246EA7;
  padding: 15px 12px 15px 47px;
  background: #DFECF7 url(images/info.png) .5em .4em no-repeat;
  border: 1px solid #A7CEEC;
  -webkit-border-radius: 4px;
  -moz-border-radius: 4px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  -moz-box-shadow:0 0 6px #aaaaaa;
  -webkit-box-shadow:0 0 6px #aaaaaa;
}
.error {
  margin: 15px 0;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #C92036;
  padding: 15px 12px 15px 47px;
  background: #FAE1E1 url(images/error.png) .5em .4em no-repeat;
  border: 1px solid #EDA8A8;
  -webkit-border-radius: 4px;
  -moz-border-radius: 4px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  -moz-box-shadow:0 0 6px #aaaaaa;
  box-shadow:0 0 6px #aaaaaa;
  -webkit-box-shadow:0 0 6px #aaaaaa;
}
.warning {
  margin: 15px 0;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #E08820;
  padding: 15px 12px 15px 47px;
  background: #FDF4D7 url(images/warning.png) .5em .4em no-repeat;
  border: 1px solid #E8C779;
  -webkit-border-radius: 4px;
  -moz-border-radius: 4px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  -moz-box-shadow:0 0 6px #aaaaaa;
  box-shadow:0 0 6px #aaaaaa;
  -webkit-box-shadow:0 0 6px #aaaaaa;
}

@-webkit-keyframes fadeIn { from {opacity:0;} to {opacity:1;}}
@-moz-keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity:0; } to { opacity:1; }}
@keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity:0; } to { opacity:1; }}

@-webkit-keyframes bargraph { 0% {width:0%}}
@-moz-keyframes bargraph { 0% { width:0; }}
@-ms-keyframes bargraph {0% {width:0}}
@keyframes bargraph { 0% { width:0; }}

.bar-anim {

	-webkit-animation:bargraph ease-in-out 1;
	-moz-animation:bargraph ease-in-out 1;
        -ms-animation:bargraph ease-in-out 1;
	animation:bargraph ease-in-out 1;
	-ms-animation-fill-mode:forwards;
	-webkit-animation-fill-mode:forwards;
	-moz-animation-fill-mode:forwards;
        animation-fill-mode:forwards;
	-webkit-animation-duration:2s;
	-moz-animation-duration:2s;
        -ms-animation-duration:2s;
	animation-duration:2s;
	-webkit-animation-delay:0s;
	-moz-animation-delay:0s;
        -ms-animation-delay:0s;
	animation-delay:0s;

}
.fade-in {
	opacity:0;
	-webkit-animation:fadeIn ease-in 1;
	-moz-animation:fadeIn ease-in 1;
	animation:fadeIn ease-in 1;
	-webkit-animation-fill-mode:forwards;
	-moz-animation-fill-mode:forwards;
	animation-fill-mode:forwards;
	-webkit-animation-duration:.5s;
	-moz-animation-duration:.5s;
	animation-duration:.5s;
}
.fade-in.chrom {
	-webkit-animation-delay: 0.3s;
	-moz-animation-delay: 0.3s;
	animation-delay: 0.3s;
	}
.fade-in.chrom2 {
	-webkit-animation-delay: 0.4s;
	-moz-animation-delay: 0.4s;
	animation-delay: 0.4s;
	}
.fade-in.chrom3 {
	-webkit-animation-delay: 0.5s;
	-moz-animation-delay: 0.5s;
	animation-delay: 0.5s;
	}	
.fade-in.solv {
	-webkit-animation-delay: 0.6s;
	-moz-animation-delay: 0.6s;
	animation-delay: 0.6s;
	}	
.fade-in.micro {
	-webkit-animation-delay: 0.7s;
	-moz-animation-delay: 0.7s;
	animation-delay: 0.7s;
	}	
.fade-in.foreign {
	-webkit-animation-delay: 0.8s;
	-moz-animation-delay: 0.8s;
	animation-delay: 0.8s;
	}	

.fade-in.pest {
	-webkit-animation-delay: 0.9s;
	-moz-animation-delay: 0.9s;
	animation-delay: 0.9s;
	}	
.fade-in.notes {
	-webkit-animation-delay: 1s;
	-moz-animation-delay: 1s;
	animation-delay: 1s;
	}		
.fade-in.potency {
	-webkit-animation-delay: 0s;
	-moz-animation-delay: 0s;
	animation-delay: 0;
	}
	


.fade-in.terpenes {
	-webkit-animation-delay: 0.1s;
	-moz-animation-delay: 0.1s;
	animation-delay: 0.1s;
	}

.fade-in.moisture {
	-webkit-animation-delay: 0.2s;

	animation-delay: 0.2s;
	}
.fade-in.ANLheader {
